<text><body>
<lb ed="T" n="0774b20"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0774b21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0774b22" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 507</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="T" n="0774b23"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note resp="Taisho" n="0774012" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0774012">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0774012"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0774013" resp="Taisho">未生冤＝未生怨【三】下同【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0774013">未生冤【大】下同，未生怨【宋】下同【元】下同【明】下同【宮】</note><app n="0774013"><lem wit="【大】">未生冤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">未生怨</rdg></app>經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="0774b24"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0774b25"/><byline cb:type="Translator">吳<note n="0774014" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔月支國居士〕－【宋】【元】，〔國〕－【宮】</note><note n="0774014" type="mod" resp="CBETA">月支國居士【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】，月支居士【宮】</note><app n="0774014"><lem wit="【大】">月支國<note n="0774015" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">居士＝優婆塞【明】【宮】</note><note n="0774015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">居士【大】，優婆塞【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774015"><lem wit="【大】">居士</lem><rdg wit="【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">優婆塞</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">月支居士</rdg></app>支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0774b26" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0774b2601">聞如是：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0774b2604">一時，佛在王舍國雞山中。諸天，龍，鬼
<lb ed="T" n="0774b27"/>神，帝王，臣民，皆詣佛所，稽首，承風，供養之
<lb n="0774b28" ed="T"/>儀靡不盡禮。調達覩之，其嫉無量，還告太
<lb ed="T" n="0774b29"/>子未生冤曰：「汝父輦國眾寶以貢佛，諸沙門，
<pb ed="T" n="0774c" xml:id="T14.0507.0774c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0774c01"/>國藏空竭。可早圖之，即位為王，吾當興師
<lb n="0774c02" ed="T"/>往征佛也。子可為王，吾當為佛，兩得其所，
<lb ed="T" n="0774c03"/>不亦善乎！子必成之。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0774c0309">未生冤與調達結斯
<lb n="0774c04" ed="T"/>陰謀已，則勅秉勢臣，令勒兵：「王還，奪其<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0774016" type="orig">印＝即【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0774016" type="mod">印【大】，即【明】</note><app n="0774016"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0774c05"/>綬以付獄。」王還，臣即如命，以王付獄。王意
<lb ed="T" n="0774c06"/>恬然，照之宿殃，心無恐懼，重信佛言。王曰：
<lb n="0774c07" ed="T"/>「吾有何過而罪我乎？」皇后、貴人率土巨細，
<lb ed="T" n="0774c08"/>莫不哀慟。王顧謂哭者曰：「佛說天地、日月、須
<lb n="0774c09" ed="T"/>彌山海有成必敗，盛者即衰，合會有離，生
<lb ed="T" n="0774c10"/>者必死。由之憂悲輪轉無際，以致重苦。尋
<lb n="0774c11" ed="T"/>其<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0774017" resp="Taisho">原＝源【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0774017">原【大】，源【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774017"><lem wit="【大】">原</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">源</rdg></app>，察其始，因緣合會即有，謂之生；因緣
<lb n="0774c12" ed="T"/>離散即滅，謂之空。<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0774018">夫＝天【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0774018">夫【大】，天【宮】</note><app n="0774018"><lem wit="【大】">夫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">天</rdg></app>身者四大耳，眾生魂
<lb ed="T" n="0774c13"/>靈寄處其中，死還其本，魂靈空去，謂之非
<lb ed="T" n="0774c14"/>身。身尚<note resp="Taisho" n="0774019" place="foot text" type="orig">不＋（可）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0774019" type="mod" resp="CBETA">不【大】，不可【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774019"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不可</rdg></app>保，何國之常守乎？佛初入國，吾
<lb ed="T" n="0774c15"/>未有子也。問吾：『寧知當來王不乎？』吾對曰：『不
<lb ed="T" n="0774c16"/>知。』世尊重曰：『一切無常，汝諦思之。』佛之誡
<lb ed="T" n="0774c17"/>我，正為今也。各努力建志，懷存佛誡矣。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0774c1716">王
<lb ed="T" n="0774c18"/>謂太子曰：「汝每有疾，吾為燋心，欲以身命
<lb ed="T" n="0774c19"/><note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0774020" resp="Taisho">救＝受【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0774020">救【大】，受【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774020"><lem wit="【大】">救</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">受</rdg></app>危代汝。親之仁恩，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0774021" type="orig">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0774021" type="mod" resp="CBETA">唯【大】＊，惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0774021"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>天為上。汝懷何
<lb n="0774c20" ed="T"/>心，忍為<note resp="Taisho" n="0774022" place="foot text" type="orig">逆惡＝惡逆【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0774022" resp="CBETA">逆惡【大】，惡逆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0774022"><lem wit="【大】">逆惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惡逆</rdg></app>乎？夫殺親者，死入太山，不中
<lb n="0774c21" ed="T"/>止息，汝將當之也。吾是汝尊，重親尊孝尚
<lb ed="T" n="0774c22"/>恐名不稱，豈況殺父乎？以國惠汝，吾欲至佛
<lb ed="T" n="0774c23"/>所作沙門。吾觀婬<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0774023">妷＝泆【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0774023" resp="CBETA">妷【大】，泆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0774023"><lem wit="【大】">妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">泆</rdg></app>猶火燒身，女類之好
<lb ed="T" n="0774c24"/>以為虛空，無目之徒靡不惑焉！唯覩佛經，照
<lb n="0774c25" ed="T"/>女偽之尤惡，知榮利之害身。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0774c2512">太子曰：「汝莫
<lb ed="T" n="0774c26"/>多云。吾獲宿願，豈有赦哉？」勅獄吏曰：「絕其
<lb ed="T" n="0774c27"/>餉食，以餓殺之。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0774c2707">有司將入獄，<note n="0774024" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">汫＝缾【三】，萍【宮】</note><note n="0774024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">洴【大】，缾【宋】【元】【明】，萍【宮】</note><app n="0774024"><lem wit="【大】">洴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">缾</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">萍</rdg></app>沙王向佛
<lb n="0774c28" ed="T"/>所在，稽首重拜曰：「子有天地之惡，吾無絲
<lb ed="T" n="0774c29"/>髮之忿心矣。<app corresp="#0774021" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>存佛教：世無常樂，其苦
<pb xml:id="T14.0507.0775a" ed="T" n="0775a"/>
<lb n="0775a01" ed="T"/>有長。」入獄被髮，仰天呼曰：「痛乎！天豈有斯
<lb n="0775a02" ed="T"/>道哉？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a0203" rend="inline">后、妃、貴人舉國巨細，靡不哀慟。后謂
<lb ed="T" n="0775a03"/>太子曰：「大王掠桎梏，處牢獄，坐臥須人，其
<lb n="0775a04" ed="T"/>痛難言。自汝生來，大王赤心，懸情于汝，食
<lb n="0775a05" ed="T"/>息不忘，四大盈<note place="foot text" n="0775001" type="orig" resp="Taisho">縮＝宿【宮】</note><note n="0775001" type="mod" resp="CBETA">縮【大】，宿【宮】</note><app n="0775001"><lem wit="【大】">縮</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">宿</rdg></app>，<note resp="Taisho" n="0775002" place="foot text" type="orig">枕＝旃【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0775002" resp="CBETA">枕【大】，旃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775002"><lem wit="【大】">枕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">旃</rdg></app>伏臨汝，涕泗交并，
<lb ed="T" n="0775a06"/>心燋體枯，欲以身命代爾殞矣。當存天人之
<lb ed="T" n="0775a07"/>育，無為逆也。佛說經云：『夫善之極者，莫大
<lb n="0775a08" ed="T"/>於孝；惡之大<note place="foot text" n="0775003" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0775003" resp="CBETA">者【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775003"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，其<app corresp="#0774021" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>害親乎！』長幼相事，
<lb n="0775a09" ed="T"/>天當祐之，豈況親哉？汝順<note place="foot text" n="0775004" type="orig" resp="Taisho">凶＝兇【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0775004" type="mod">凶【大】，兇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0775004"><lem wit="【大】">凶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">兇</rdg></app>虐，為斯重惡，
<lb ed="T" n="0775a10"/>必入太山——世間六十億年為太山一日一夕——
<lb n="0775a11" ed="T"/>所更諸毒每處有年。汝其畢之，不亦難乎？
<lb n="0775a12" ed="T"/>夫快心之士，無不後悔。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775a1210">太子曰：「吾少小有
<lb ed="T" n="0775a13"/>志殺父為王，今日獲願，何諫之云乎？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775a1315">后曰：
<lb ed="T" n="0775a14"/>「夫不用諫者，亡國之基矣！吾欲見大王，寧
<lb ed="T" n="0775a15"/>可不乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1504" rend="inline">太子曰：「可。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775a1508">后淨身澡浴，以蜜<g ref="#CB00595"/>塗
<lb ed="T" n="0775a16"/>身，入見大王，面顏瘦痟不識。舉哀，聞之者莫
<lb ed="T" n="0775a17"/>不揮淚，后曰：「佛說榮樂無常，罪苦有恒。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1716" rend="inline">王曰：
<lb n="0775a18" ed="T"/>「獄吏絕餉食，飢渴日久。身八<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775005" resp="Taisho">萬＝十【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0775005" resp="CBETA">萬【大】，十【宮】</note><app n="0775005"><lem wit="【大】">萬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">十</rdg></app>戶，戶有數
<lb n="0775a19" ed="T"/>百種蟲，擾吾腹中。血肉消盡，壽命且窮矣！」
<lb ed="T" n="0775a20"/>言之哽咽，息絕復連。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775a2009">后曰：「具照斯<note place="foot text" n="0775006" type="orig" resp="Taisho">艱＝難【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0775006">艱【大】，難【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0775006"><lem wit="【大】">艱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">難</rdg></app>。妾以
<lb ed="T" n="0775a21"/><g ref="#CB00595"/>蜜塗身，可就食之。當惟佛誡，無忽也。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775a2116">王
<lb n="0775a22" ed="T"/>食畢，向佛所在，哽咽稽首曰：「佛說榮福難保，
<lb n="0775a23" ed="T"/>如幻如夢，誠如尊教！」謂后曰：「吾為王時，國
<lb n="0775a24" ed="T"/>土廣大，衣食從好；而今處獄，當就餓死。子所
<lb n="0775a25" ed="T"/>從得桀逆之師，違佛仁教。吾不懼死，唯恨不
<lb ed="T" n="0775a26"/>面稟佛清化，與<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0775007">鶖鷺＝秋露【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0775007">鶖鷺【大】，秋露【宮】</note><app n="0775007"><lem wit="【大】">鶖鷺</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">秋露</rdg></app>子，目連，大迦葉講尊
<lb ed="T" n="0775a27"/>道奧耳！」王重謂后曰：「佛說恩愛猶若眾鳥會
<lb ed="T" n="0775a28"/>栖于樹，晨各離散，隨其殃福。目連眾垢已
<lb ed="T" n="0775a29"/>除，諸惡已滅，得<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775008">于＝大【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0775008">于【大】，大【宮】</note><app n="0775008"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>六通，四達，尚為貪嫉梵
<pb xml:id="T14.0507.0775b" ed="T" n="0775b"/>
<lb n="0775b01" ed="T"/>志所捶，豈況吾哉？為殃惡追人，猶影尋身，
<lb ed="T" n="0775b02"/>響之應聲。佛時難遇，<note n="0775009" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">神化＝佛法【明】</note><note n="0775009" type="mod" resp="CBETA">神化【大】，佛法【明】</note><app n="0775009"><lem wit="【大】">神化</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">佛法</rdg></app>難聞，賢眾行高，
<lb n="0775b03" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0775010" resp="Taisho">儀式＝儀誡【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0775010" resp="CBETA">儀式【大】，儀誡【宮】</note><app n="0775010"><lem wit="【大】">儀式</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">儀誡</rdg></app>無量，非世<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775011">濡＝俗【明】，儒【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0775011" type="mod">儒【CB】【麗-CB】【宮】，濡【大】，俗【明】</note><app n="0775011"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">儒<note type="cf1">K20n0821_p1134a10</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">濡</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">俗</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">儒</rdg></app>所能履行。懷佛經典，以
<lb ed="T" n="0775b04"/>仁化民；獲供養之福，稟其清化，誠亦難值
<lb ed="T" n="0775b05"/>哉！吾今死矣，遷神遠逝。夫欲建志，莫尚佛
<lb ed="T" n="0775b06"/>教也。汝慎守之，防來禍矣！」后聞王誡，重又
<lb n="0775b07" ed="T"/>哀慟。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775b0703">太子詰獄吏曰：「絕王食有日，不死何
<lb n="0775b08" ed="T"/>為？」對曰：「皇后入獄，有<g ref="#CB00595"/>蜜之貢，以延王命。」太
<lb ed="T" n="0775b09"/>子曰：「自今莫令后見王。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b0910" rend="inline">王飢，勢起向佛所在
<lb ed="T" n="0775b10"/>稽首，即為不飢，夜時為明。太子聞之，令塞
<lb ed="T" n="0775b11"/>窓牖，削其足底，無令得起而覩佛明。有司
<lb n="0775b12" ed="T"/>即削足底。其痛無量，念佛不忘。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b1213" rend="inline">佛遙為說經
<lb n="0775b13" ed="T"/>曰：「夫善惡行，殃福歸身，可不慎矣！」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775b1314">瓶沙王
<lb n="0775b14" ed="T"/>對曰：「若當<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775012">支＝肢【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0775012">支【大】，肢【元】【明】</note><app n="0775012"><lem wit="【大】">支</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">肢</rdg></app>解寸斬於體，終不念惡。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b1415" rend="inline">世尊
<lb n="0775b15" ed="T"/>重曰：「吾今為如來、無所著、正真道、最正覺、道
<lb ed="T" n="0775b16"/>法御、天人師，三千大千日月天神、鬼龍靡不
<lb n="0775b17" ed="T"/>稽首，宿之餘殃于今不釋，豈況凡庶？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775b1715"><note n="0775013" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">王＝三【宮】</note><note n="0775013" type="mod" resp="CBETA">王【大】，三【宮】</note><app n="0775013"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">三</rdg></app>受
<lb ed="T" n="0775b18"/>天中天恩，具照宿殃，不敢慍望，不懼<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0775014">大＝太【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0775014" type="mod">大【大】，太【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">太</rdg></app>山
<lb n="0775b19" ed="T"/>燒煮之罪，中心在佛及諸弟子，坐臥敢<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775015" resp="Taisho">忽＝忘【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0775015">忽【大】，忘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775015"><lem wit="【大】">忽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忘</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0775b20" ed="T"/>即叉手稽首：「今日命絕，永替神化。」<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775016" resp="Taisho">喐＝都【宋】【元】，那【明】，噢【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0775016" resp="CBETA">喐【大】，都【宋】【元】，那【明】，噢【宮】</note><app n="0775016"><lem wit="【大】">喐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">都</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">那</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">噢</rdg></app>咿哽
<lb ed="T" n="0775b21"/><note resp="Taisho" n="0775017" place="foot text" type="orig">咽＝喳【三】【宮】</note><note n="0775017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">咽【大】，喳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775017"><lem wit="【大】">咽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">喳</rdg></app>，斯須息絕。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0775b2106">舉國臣民靡不躃踊，呼天奈
<lb ed="T" n="0775b22"/>何。瓶沙王即得道迹，上生天上，三道門塞，
<lb ed="T" n="0775b23"/>諸苦都滅矣！</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0775b24" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="001"><cb:jhead><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0775018">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0775018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0775018"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>未生冤<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0775019" resp="Taisho">經＋（一卷）【宋】【元】</note><note type="mod" n="0775019" resp="CBETA">經【大】，經一卷【宋】【元】</note><app n="0775019"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">經一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
